&lt;p&gt;图片垃圾内容检测：&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9oZWxwLmFsaXl1bi5jb20vZG9jdW1lbnRfZGV0YWlsLzcwMjkyLmh0bWw/c3BtPWEyYzRnLjExMTg2NjIzLjYuNjE2LjVkN2QxZTdmOXZEUno0&#34;&gt;https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/70292.html?spm=a2c4g.11186623.6.616.5d7d1e7f9vDRz4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
